Harry Spear https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_Spear 0 Harry Spear (December 16, 1921 – September 22, 2006) was an American child actor, notable for appearing in the Our Gang short subjects series from 1927 to 1929. He was a native of Los Angeles, California.
